entries.title: BT customer contracts face probe by regulator
entries.description: Ofcom says it is looking into whether two BT companies, EE and Plusnet, have breached rules.

entries.title: Microsoft extends AI partnership with ChatGPT and Dall-E maker OpenAI
entries.description: It announces a "multi-year, multibillion dollar investment" with OpenAI to accelerate breakthroughs.

entries.title: Spotify cuts jobs in latest tech-sector cull
entries.description: The music-streaming company says it is shedding 6% of its workforce.

entries.title: Merriam-Webster buys Wordle-style hit game Quordle
entries.description: US dictionary publisher Merriam-Webster buys Quordle, a Wordle-style five-letter-word guessing game.
